<plot>Young Heroes is the very first recruitment documentary made about City Year's Young Heroes Program used nationally and internationally. Young Heroes Program is a special program designed for middle school aged youths who come to the city every Saturday morning during the months of January until May learning about key topics such as hunger and homelessness, drugs in the community and violence. In the afternoon these students go out and perform community service for the city related to the topic of the day.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?667055</url></doc>
